-- HealthSouth in deal to sell rehabilitation division
-- 
-- Mon Jan 29, 2007 7:18am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/01/29/us-healthsouth-idUSWEN295320070129

 

 CHICAGO  (Reuters) - HealthSouth Corp. ( HLS.N ) on Monday said it has reached a deal with Select Medical Corporation to sell its outpatient rehabilitation division for about $245 million. 

 Select Medical Corporation is a privately owned operator of specialty hospitals and outpatient rehabilitation facilities. The transaction is expected to be completed in 60 to 90 days, HealthSouth said in a statement.